            {
                id = "0", speaker = "The Mythallar-Keeper",
                text = "*(In the heart of the enclave, a vast crystalline engine pulses — the mythallar, the artifact that holds the whole city aloft — and its light is *wrong*, stuttering amber where it should burn white. A calm woman in keeper's robes makes small adjustments, and as nobles hurry past she calls out, warm and certain:)* \"A momentary flux, my lords! The mythallar is *recalibrating* — perfectly routine! Do enjoy the evening!\" *(they relax; they move on; they believe her. Then she sees you watching, and the warmth on her face does not change at all, but her eyes — her eyes tell you that she knows you know.)*",
